13
00:01:22.875 --> 00:01:25.083
-Joyce!
-You're hitting your wife?

14
00:01:25.166 --> 00:01:27.041
-Jo!
-Listen here. I said listen here.

15
00:01:28.291 --> 00:01:31.250
You're my wife. you hear me?
I'm not your piece of shit!

16
00:01:31.333 --> 00:01:32.416
Do you hear me?

17
00:01:33.000 --> 00:01:37.583
You and I will be separated by death.

18
00:01:38.083 --> 00:01:41.291
You hear me? We're going to be
separated by death. you and I. Joyce.

19
00:01:41.375 --> 00:01:43.333
Do you hear me?

20
00:02:10.750 --> 00:02:11.750
