Joyce.

258
00:16:51.833 --> 00:16:53.000
It's cold.

259
00:16:53.958 --> 00:16:56.208
I'm feeling cold. Joyce.

260
00:17:02.708 --> 00:17:05.541
I can't put another blanket on you.

261
00:17:06.583 --> 00:17:08.750
I mean. you're sweating already.

262
00:17:14.416 --> 00:17:15.875
Please climb into bed with me.

263
00:17:19.416 --> 00:17:21.833
Please. Joyce.

264
00:17:36.208 --> 00:17:37.291
Thank you.

265
00:17:39.750 --> 00:17:42.166
Thank you. Joyce.

266
00:17:45.708 --> 00:17:47.541
I have a request.

267
00:17:49.208 --> 00:17:50.625
Please forgive me.

268
00:17:51.958 --> 00:17:54.375
For everything I've done to you.

269
00:17:59.958 --> 00:18:02.000
Joyce. I'm scared.

270
00:18:03.000 --> 00:18:05.416
I'm going to leave you here on Earth.

271
00:18:07.583 --> 00:18:08.833
I'm really scared.

272
00:18:10.458 --> 00:18:13.541
I'm scared. Joyce.

273
00:18:22.000 --> 00:18:25.708
Jo. you need to stop talking now.

274
00:18:27.416 --> 00:18:30.125
You and I don't have
much time left together.

275
00:18:32.375 --> 00:18:35.500
Let's just lay here.

276
00:18:35.583 --> 00:18:36.833
Together.

277
00:18:39.166 --> 00:18:40.375
You and I.

278
00:18:43.166 --> 00:18:46.125
J and J.

279
00:18:49.125 --> 00:18:51.666
Just the way it was always meant to be.

280
00:19:02.416 --> 00:19:03.875
Is there a bun in the oven?

281
00:19:03.958 --> 00:19:06.625
-Is this our little Mlungisi Gomora?
-Oh. stop.

282
00:19:06.708 --> 00:19:07.708
There we go.

283
00:19:08.375 --> 00:19:09.708
I'm proud of you.

284
00:19:09.791 --> 00:19:11.500
We did this.

285
00:19:11.583 --> 00:19:13.166
-Together.
-Together.

286
00:19:22.125 --> 00:19:24.458
Yes.

287
00:19:26.083 --> 00:19:28.333
-Mmm.
-Is that my name I hear?

288
00:19:28.416 --> 00:19:32.375
Thank you.

289
00:19:34.125 --> 00:19:36.833
Don't forget to come back with
something nice for Nkazi.

290
00:19:36.916 --> 00:19:38.083
Damn.

291
00:19:38.166 --> 00:19:40.291
This suitcase is already heavy.

292
00:19:40.375 --> 00:19:42.416
-Oh. well.
-You're the one who packed it.

293
00:19:52.833 --> 00:19:54.333
Mr Gomora!

294
00:19:54.416 --> 00:19:57.375
Oh. my! Oh. my! Mr Gomora! Mr Gomora!

295
00:19:58.875 --> 00:20:01.375
Mr Gomora is no more.

296
00:20:01.458 --> 00:20:03.625
What's wrong? Dad?

297
00:20:03.708 --> 00:20:05.916
Dad! Dad!

298
00:20:06.000 --> 00:20:07.958
Ntombi. what happened? Wake him up!

299
00:20:08.041 --> 00:20:10.833
-I don't know. I don't know!
-Ntombi. make him wake up!

300
00:20:10.916 --> 00:20:13.500
-This cannot be happening? Oh. my God!
-Oh. my goodness!

301
00:20:13.583 --> 00:20:16.250
-Dad! Ntombi!
-I'm trying to save him! Help!

302
00:20:16.333 --> 00:20:18.625
Oh. no!

303
00:20:19.791 --> 00:20:21.500
Quick. get the ambulance. please!

304
00:20:21.583 --> 00:20:23.958
Oh. my God. Where's the phone?
